[Name] Glade
[Summary] GUI builder for GTK+ and GNOME
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL)
[Description] Glade is a GUI builder for GTK+ and GNOME. It stores projects in an XML format and can generate C code from this meta-format. Additionally, the meta-format can be converted to other languages via modules. For example, glade-- can generate C++ code.
[Homepage] https://glade.gnome.org/
